  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that the name of Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Rigney\" title=\"Rigney\">Rigney</a>, who claims history is a wheel, refers to <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Jordan\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Robert Jordan\">Robert Jordan</a>, author of the <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wheel_of_Time\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Wheel of Time\">Wheel of Time</a></i> fantasy series, whose real name is James Rigney?<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/104&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/FAQ/Entry/Are_there_any_nods_to_other_works_in_the_series\">Are there any nods to other works in the series?</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404051055\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.005 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.006 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 32/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 190/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 114/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 3/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 469/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    